_sText:
Updated for the 4HM Gun Game Mod by ivix <http://www.bahamutzero.com>:
(most) weapons, buyzones, bomb sites, and hostages have been removed.

Spawn points: 26

==========================
Original fy_area_762a.txt:

FY_Area_762a

By Android X

Install instructions:
    Just copy "fy_area_762a.bsp" to the "maps" folder located were you installed counter strike source.

Note:
    Has 26 spawn points cause it's a small map. Have fun!
    Uses standard textures.
    Uses props from the prodigy map(wire spools, concrete bags) so you must have that map!

    Please report any bugs in this map. you can contact me at rowdyshadowfire@yahoo.com.au
